.TH smi-timestamp "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Utility Command"
.SH NAME
smi-timestamp \- Generate a high-resolution timestamp
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B smi-timestamp
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B smi-timestamp
prints a high-resolution timestamp in the format \fBddmmyyyyHHMMSSNS\fR (day, month, year, hour, minute, second, nanoseconds).
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
smi-timestamp
.SH AUTHOR
.PP
Command written by Imre Tabur.
Documentation written by Imre Tabur.
.SH "REPORTING BUGS"
.PP
Report smi-timestamp bugs to \fIinfo@setmy.info\fR
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.PP
.BR uuid (1)

